content:
Exporting an Intelligent Forecast in Service Cloud:

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience. Available in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.

To export: 

* Open Intelligent Forecasts from the App Launcher.
* Click to open an intelligent forecast.
* Click Export.
* Click Export to confirm.
* The CSV file downloads to your default downloads folder.

You can filter the intelligent forecast 9 different ways before export: Workload Type, Date Range, Hourly, Daily, Weekly, Channel, Region, Skill, and Custom. Note that a monthly interval is not supported for export.

The export limit is 40,000 records. If exceeded, filter data further and try again.
title: Exporting Intelligent Forecasts in Service Cloud
